OL,3,CTourist killed in huge fire at
OL,4,CCaribbean hotel as 1,700 forced to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,FA woman has been killed and almost
OL,8,F1,700 tourists have been evacuated
OL,9,Fafter a huge fire broke out at a hotel
OL,10,Fin the Dominican Republic.
OL,12,FThe Viva Dominicus Beach by Wyndham,
OL,13,Fin Bayahibe, a popular tourist
OL,14,Fdestination on the southeastern coast
OL,15,Fof the Dominican Republic, caught fire
OL,16,Fon Friday, with the blaze rapidly
OL,17,Fspreading through the resort.
OL,19,FFrancesca Valentino, a 46-year-old
OL,20,FItalian woman, was killed in the fire,
OL,21,FDominican emergency services said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
