OL,3,CTourist killed in huge fire at
OL,4,CCaribbean hotel as 1,700 forced to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThree people were hospitalised and six
OL,13,Fothers were treated at the scene,
OL,14,FITV's North American partner CNN
OL,15,Freported.
OL,17,FAuthorities said about 1,690 tourists
OL,18,Fhad to be evacuated to other hotels
OL,19,Fand nearby housing facilities on the
OL,20,FCaribbean country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
