OL,3,CTourist killed in huge fire at
OL,4,CCaribbean hotel as 1,700 forced to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,FThe cause of the blaze is under
OL,8,Finvestigation, and officials said it
OL,9,Fappeared to spread rapidly due to
OL,10,Fwindy weather and the resort's partly
OL,11,Fthatched roof.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
