OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782054673
OL,3,CTourist killed in huge fire at
OL,4,CCaribbean hotel as 1,700 forced to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,F"It has been observed that the fire
OL,8,Fspread rapidly due to the nature of
OL,9,Fpart of the roof structure made with
OL,10,Fcana (dry palm leaf) as well as the
OL,11,Fwind conditions present in the area,
OL,12,Ffactors that would have contributed to
OL,13,Fthe expansion of the flames," said
OL,14,FGeneral Manuel Mendez, director of the
OL,15,FEmergency Operation Center, at a press
OL,16,Fconference.
OL,18,FThe COE did not immediately report
OL,19,Fpeople injured or killed by the fire.
