OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782054673
OL,3,CTourist killed in huge fire at
OL,4,CCaribbean hotel as 1,700 forced to
OL,5,Cevacuate
OL,7,F"As part of actions to protect the
OL,8,Flife and safety of people,
OL,9,Fapproximately 1,690 guests were
OL,10,Fevacuated from the hotel Viva Wyndham
OL,11,FDominicus Beach, who have been
OL,12,Frelocated to nearby hotels and other
OL,13,Ffacilities enabled to ensure their
OL,14,Fwell-being," Mendez said.
